        "body": "## Requirements\r\n- [x] This PR has a title that briefly describes the work done including the ticket number. If there is a ticket, make sure your PR title includes a conventional commit label. See existing PR titles for inspiration.\r\n- [ ] My work is based on designs, which are linked or shown either in the Jira ticket or the description below.\r\n- [x] My work includes tests or is validated by existing tests.\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\nFixes [O3-4217](https://openmrs.atlassian.net/browse/O3-4217)\r\n\r\nAs highlighted in SDK-360, the `distro.properties` file was missing several explicit dependency declarations, relying on separate files and Dockerfile ARGs instead of being the single source of truth for the distribution.\r\n\r\nChanges made:\r\n- Added `omod.spa=${spa.version}` to both `distro.properties` and `distro-no-demo.properties` — the SPA backend OMOD was not declared at all\r\n- Added `spa.core=next` — app shell version was previously only set via `ARG APP_SHELL_VERSION=next` in `frontend/Dockerfile`\r\n- Added all 44 `spa.frontendModules.@openmrs/esm-*=next` entries — frontend modules were previously only defined in `frontend/spa-assemble-config.json`\r\n- Added `<spa.version>2.1.0</spa.version>` version property and `spa-omod` Maven dependency in `pom.xml`\r\n\r\n`frontend/spa-assemble-config.json` and `frontend/Dockerfile` are intentionally left unchanged. Version pinning for frontend modules will be addressed in a follow-up.\r\n\r\n## Screenshots\r\nN/A — no UI changes.\r\n\r\n## Related Issue\r\n[O3-4217](https://openmrs.atlassian.net/browse/O3-4217)\r\n\r\n## Other\r\nN/A\n\n[O3-4217]: https://openmrs.atlassian.net/browse/O3-4217?atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNWRkNTljNzYxNjVmNDY3MDlhMDU5Y2ZhYzA5YTRkZjUiLCJwIjoiZ2l0aHViLWNvbS1KU1cifQ\n[O3-4217]: https://openmrs.atlassian.net/browse/O3-4217?atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNWRkNTljNzYxNjVmNDY3MDlhMDU5Y2ZhYzA5YTRkZjUiLCJwIjoiZ2l0aHViLWNvbS1KU1cifQ",
