        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\nThis PR refines the UI, improves navigation consistency, and updates content on the Rules page across the SkillFest platform.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n### UI & Styling\r\n- **Text selection** — Updated global `::selection` styling to use black background with white text\r\n- **Hamburger menu** — Fixed hamburger icon visibility and behavior on small screens\r\n\r\n### Rules Page\r\n- Built out the full Rules page with all 5 sections — Eligibility, Participation Rules, Scoring System, Code of Conduct, and Disqualification\r\n- Added scoring table with all 5 difficulty tiers (Beginner Friendly → Extreme) and point values\r\n- Added info callout in Section 01 clarifying that NST-SDC Developer Club applications are handled exclusively via the Fresher Track\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Type of Change\r\n\r\n- [x] Bug fix\r\n- [x] UI improvement\r\n- [ ] New feature\r\n- [x] Content update\r\n\r\n## Summary by Sourcery\r\n\r\nUpdate navigation and layout to support a new Rules page while refining selection styling and scroll behavior.\r\n\r\nNew Features:\r\n- Add a dedicated Rules page outlining eligibility, participation, scoring, code of conduct, and disqualification policies for SkillFest.\r\n- Introduce an automatic scroll-to-top behavior on route changes across the app.\r\n\r\nBug Fixes:\r\n- Improve navbar link and hamburger icon visibility and behavior on scroll and mobile.\r\n- Ensure footer platform links scroll the page back to the top when navigating.\r\n\r\nEnhancements:\r\n- Add Rules entry to the main navbar and refine mobile drawer spacing.\r\n- Update footer social links to point to GitHub and support email, and simplify the footer’s lower section layout.\r\n- Change global text selection styling to use a high-contrast black background with white text for better readability.\r\n\r\nDocumentation:\r\n- Document event rules and guidelines directly in the UI via the new Rules page.\r\n\r\n##Changed Images\r\n<img width=\"405\" height=\"801\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-04-10 at 9 17 36 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5126afdf-fa7c-4a83-8a2e-2d8e002b0baa\" />\r\nmade hamburger icon visible for the mobile screens.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"665\" height=\"50\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-04-10 at 9 18 11 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e2d32704-49c9-4a15-a280-a0f0fbc0630a\" />\r\nAdded Rules in navigation bar\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1512\" height=\"982\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-04-10 at 9 18 47 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2dd815d3-b60b-427f-b842-629431d187f0\" />\r\nAdded Rules Page\r\n\r\n\r\n<img width=\"493\" height=\"249\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-04-10 at 9 19 12 PM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/904814fe-fa0d-4cdd-9636-73b29f2eb2e4\" />\r\nmade changes in footer redirection links",
